title: MOTHXR - Centerfold (2016)
description:
Mothxr is a four-piece alternative band from Brooklyn, led by actor/artist Penn Badgley (Gossip Girl, Margin Call, Greetings from Tim Buckley). In May 2015, their top ten Hype Machine track, Easy, secured them the #1 spot on Billboard & Twitter s Emerging Artist charts.

MOTHXR has sold out headline shows in New York, LA, London and Paris, and previously toured with San Cisco, Sir Sly, Har Mar Superstar and Streets of Laredo.The band recently played Montauk s Surf Lodge Music Series as well as the first ever Full Moon Festival in Brooklyn.

Centerfold is the band's debut album.
